'''Galactic City Spaceport''' was, for several [[Standard century/Legends|centuries]] before the start of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the primary [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Its role as the [[City/Legends|city's]] primary spaceport was replaced after the creation of [[Chancellor Palpatine Spaceport]]; however, after the new site's construction, many [[Senator/Legends|senators]] continued to use the Galactic City Spaceport to avoid the hustle of the newer location.

During the Clone Wars, it was the location of a [[Galactic City spaceport hostage siege|hostage incident]] involving [[Korun/Legends|Korunnai]] [[Terrorist/Legends|terrorists]].

